760
01:09:39,228 --> 01:09:40,991
Why didn't you tell me?

761
01:09:41,063 --> 01:09:43,793
Steve, I didn't want you to
get worried.

762
01:09:45,301 --> 01:09:46,928
Daddy, come here!

763
01:09:47,303 --> 01:09:49,737
