766
01:09:54,310 --> 01:09:57,074
You're a fucking asshole, man. Both of you.

767
01:09:59,048 --> 01:10:00,140
What, Jeremy?

768
01:10:06,422 --> 01:10:08,822
There's nothing in this guitar case.

769
01:10:10,326 --> 01:10:12,089
All right, where's the money?

770
01:10:15,798 --> 01:10:18,733
Son, you'd better tell me where the money is.

771
01:10:18,801 --> 01:10:23,431
You're never going to find it without me,
so we might as well make a deal.

772
01:10:24,807 --> 01:10:26,900
Jimmy, turn the car around.

773
01:10:34,350 --> 01:10:36,079
Where are we going?

774
01:10:36,218 --> 01:10:39,585
Back to your friend's place
and kill everybody there.

775
01:10:45,861 --> 01:10:47,192
All right.

776
01:10:48,230 --> 01:10:49,254
Damn it.

777
01:10:49,966 --> 01:10:52,025
There ain't nobody down there.

778
01:10:52,134 --> 01:10:53,999
- Who are you calling?
- The police.

779
01:10:54,136 --> 01:10:56,229
You can't do that. Hang up the phone.

780
01:10:56,305 --> 01:10:58,364
- Why?
- Jesse has a shitload of drug money.

781
01:10:58,441 --> 01:10:59,874
You can't involve the cops.

782
01:10:59,942 --> 01:11:02,740
I'm not sure stealing money from criminals
is a crime.

783
01:11:02,812 --> 01:11:04,609
If they arrest him, he'll be alive.

784
01:11:04,680 --> 01:11:08,138
Listen, if this ain't handled right,
Jesse's going to wind up dead.

785
01:11:08,217 --> 01:11:09,912
Hang up that fuckin' phone.

786
01:11:16,192 --> 01:11:17,921
What are you doing?

787
01:11:21,197 --> 01:11:23,062
I've got a family to think about.

788
01:11:23,232 --> 01:11:25,530
Nobody's asking you to come along.

789
01:11:25,601 --> 01:11:28,126
Where? You don't know where they're going.

790
01:11:28,204 --> 01:11:29,330
Sure, I do.

791
01:11:29,405 --> 01:11:32,135
They'll make Jesse take them
where he buried the money.

792
01:11:32,208 --> 01:11:35,302
If you were him,
where would you bury that money?

793
01:11:38,347 --> 01:11:40,247
I'm going to need your boat.

794
01:11:42,952 --> 01:11:45,921
- How far away is this fuckin' island?
- About half an hour.

795
01:11:46,188 --> 01:11:49,089
- How do we get there? Swim?
- I got a boat.

796
01:11:50,126 --> 01:11:52,651
There ain't nobody out there.
This place is closed.

797
01:11:52,728 --> 01:11:54,286
I have the keys. I know the owner.

798
01:11:54,363 --> 01:11:57,457
You wouldn't be lying to us,
would you, skipper?

799
01:11:58,334 --> 01:11:59,824
He called him "skipper."

800
01:12:03,439 --> 01:12:04,599
Honey?

801
01:12:06,976 --> 01:12:08,500
What's the matter?

802
01:12:08,677 --> 01:12:09,905
Nothing.

803
01:12:13,949 --> 01:12:16,315
- It's okay, Mommy.
- What's going on?

804
01:12:16,585 --> 01:12:18,382
Daddy's playing with his friends.

805
01:12:24,427 --> 01:12:27,362
It seems pretty rough out past the breakwater.

806
01:12:27,496 --> 01:12:29,987
What do you want me to do about it?

807
01:12:51,587 --> 01:12:54,750
You know how this works, right?
Just fire and pump.

808
01:12:55,724 --> 01:12:57,248
I'm not touching that thing.

809
01:12:57,326 --> 01:13:00,989
I'm taking you to the island, but that's it.
I'm staying with the boat.

810
01:13:01,097 --> 01:13:04,191
God damn it! This is for just in case. Take it.

811
01:13:07,470 --> 01:13:11,065
You're happy about this?
You might get a chance to shoot people.

812
01:13:11,140 --> 01:13:13,005
You act like I want this to happen.

813
01:13:13,075 --> 01:13:14,975
- You said it.
- That's bullshit!

814
01:13:24,920 --> 01:13:25,909
That's it.

815
01:13:30,693 --> 01:13:34,254
- Fuckin' psycho.
- Think what you want. I don't give a shit.

816
01:13:36,765 --> 01:13:40,223
Let's go. Calvin, get that shovel
and that flashlight.

817
01:13:45,107 --> 01:13:49,237
- I'm in a different position here.
- You got to do what you got to do.

818
01:13:49,478 --> 01:13:53,915
I got to do what I got to do.
Get me out there, I'll take care of the rest.

819
01:13:56,652 --> 01:14:00,053
You little fuck, you caused me a lot
of trouble. Where's my money?

820
01:14:00,122 --> 01:14:01,851
The other side of the island.

821
01:14:01,924 --> 01:14:04,256
What the fuck are we doing on this side, then?

822
01:14:04,326 --> 01:14:07,090
The boat would've capsized on the other side...

823
01:14:07,163 --> 01:14:09,028
...and we would've drowned, idiot!

824
01:14:09,098 --> 01:14:11,999
- Who's the idiot?
- God damn it!

825
01:14:12,201 --> 01:14:14,999
You want me to blow your fuckin' brains out?

826
01:14:15,204 --> 01:14:18,367
Let's go. You lead the way, Jesse.
Give him a flashlight.

827
01:14:18,440 --> 01:14:21,807
- Take this, boy.
- Louis, give me that flashlight.

828
01:14:38,027 --> 01:14:40,325
Where the hell is he taking us?

829
01:14:43,766 --> 01:14:47,930
- Can't this thing go any faster?
- Not in this weather.

830
01:14:50,506 --> 01:14:53,441
- Move!
- Move that little pissant along!

831
01:14:57,947 --> 01:14:59,437
We were right.

832
01:15:04,954 --> 01:15:07,650
I need you to keep your fuckin' eyes peeled.

833
01:15:07,723 --> 01:15:10,692
You see any crazy shit go down,
you get your ass out of here.

834
01:15:12,628 --> 01:15:15,893
This little punk is either jerking us off
or we're lost.

835
01:15:15,965 --> 01:15:18,160
I've never been here at night before.

836
01:15:18,234 --> 01:15:21,294
You fuckin' find the money, punk!
You understand me?

837
01:15:21,370 --> 01:15:22,928
Get the fuck out of here!

838
01:15:23,038 --> 01:15:25,006
We'll see you real soon.

839
01:15:28,611 --> 01:15:30,943
You don't know how many of them there are.

840
01:15:31,347 --> 01:15:34,510
They're not going to be packing
what I'm packing.

841
01:15:52,735 --> 01:15:54,498
All right! Come on.

842
01:16:06,515 --> 01:16:08,415
This whole thing sucks!

843
01:16:09,785 --> 01:16:11,878
This better be it, asshole.

844
01:16:14,723 --> 01:16:15,690
Is this it?

845
01:16:55,931 --> 01:16:58,229
Shit! There's about 20 of them.

846
01:16:58,334 --> 01:16:59,733
I count six.

847
01:17:01,136 --> 01:17:02,933
Here's what we're going to do.

848
01:17:03,205 --> 01:17:04,968
I'll cut to the right...

849
01:17:05,207 --> 01:17:08,370
...you get on the other side of them, over there.

850
01:17:08,711 --> 01:17:10,474
You don't move until I do.

851
01:17:10,913 --> 01:17:14,474
We'll catch them in our crossfire
and cut them to pieces.

852
01:17:15,684 --> 01:17:16,946
Got that?

853
01:17:26,261 --> 01:17:28,320
What the hell's going on here?

854
01:17:28,530 --> 01:17:30,122
He's dicking us!

855
01:17:43,579 --> 01:17:45,376
All right, you fuckin' assholes!

856
01:17:49,518 --> 01:17:51,645
Drop your weapons right now!

857
01:17:58,961 --> 01:18:00,792
Drop them like he said!

858
01:18:03,298 --> 01:18:04,925
I said drop them!

859
01:18:05,367 --> 01:18:06,698
Drop them!

860
01:18:08,337 --> 01:18:09,634
Take it easy, boys.

861
01:18:25,521 --> 01:18:27,045
Son of a bitch!

862
01:18:36,565 --> 01:18:38,226
Come on! Let's go.

863
01:18:38,700 --> 01:18:39,724
Come on!

864
01:18:42,004 --> 01:18:44,939
- Shit!
- One of those fuckin' punks killed Duff.

865
01:18:51,747 --> 01:18:52,839
Shit!

866
01:18:56,652 --> 01:18:59,485
- What about Morgan?
- He said to meet us at the boat.

867
01:19:05,194 --> 01:19:07,594
You know, we could be walking into a trap.

868
01:19:07,996 --> 01:19:09,657
- We got to split up.
- Right.

869
01:19:09,731 --> 01:19:12,495
- Calvin, go on out that way.
- I'm gone.

870
01:19:12,568 --> 01:19:14,468
- I'm with you.
- Come on.

871
01:19:25,080 --> 01:19:26,945
You shot my brother!

872
01:19:28,917 --> 01:19:31,249
You're dead, you son of a bitch!

873
01:19:44,766 --> 01:19:46,028
- Hold it!
- What?

874
01:19:46,101 --> 01:19:48,626
This is stupid. Let's wait for him.

875
01:19:54,243 --> 01:19:55,301
Now!

876
01:19:58,347 --> 01:20:00,645
Come on. Shoot him.

877
01:20:15,097 --> 01:20:16,724
- Shit!
- I'm sorry.

878
01:20:17,366 --> 01:20:20,096
Damn it! If you're going to be here,
don't freeze up.

879
01:20:47,162 --> 01:20:48,390
Fuck!

880
01:21:23,932 --> 01:21:24,990
Shoot him!

881
01:21:35,544 --> 01:21:37,011
Cut your...

882
01:21:37,980 --> 01:21:39,470
You little...

883
01:21:43,218 --> 01:21:45,448
- Are you hit?
- My leg.

884
01:21:48,757 --> 01:21:51,055
Come on, let's get out of here.

885
01:21:54,496 --> 01:21:55,895
Fuck!

886
01:22:00,636 --> 01:22:03,036
- Shit, where is he?
- I don't know.

887
01:22:09,978 --> 01:22:12,276
I'm going to go back and find him.

888
01:22:19,287 --> 01:22:20,549
It's him.

889
01:22:21,189 --> 01:22:24,283
- You okay?
- Kicked them fuckers' ass, didn't we?

890
01:22:25,627 --> 01:22:28,790
- You're hit.
- Let's get the hell out of here.

891
01:22:32,000 --> 01:22:34,161
Here! Grab him. I'll be right back.

892
01:22:45,781 --> 01:22:47,908
- You know what, Steve?
- What?

893
01:22:49,017 --> 01:22:51,611
It's quiet without all those guns.

894
01:22:51,687 --> 01:22:54,212
