898
01:23:55,584 --> 01:23:57,609
Let's get him to the boat.

899
01:23:58,787 --> 01:24:00,220
Don't move me.

900
01:24:02,524 --> 01:24:05,687
Stevie boy, I knew you'd come with me,
you fuck.

901
01:24:07,529 --> 01:24:08,553
You knew?

902
01:24:09,798 --> 01:24:11,891
Of course I was going to come.

903
01:24:15,103 --> 01:24:16,434
Hang in there.

904
01:24:17,139 --> 01:24:18,197
I will.

905
01:24:20,742 --> 01:24:22,710
You hang in there, okay?

906
01:24:26,548 --> 01:24:27,537
I will.

907
01:24:29,151 --> 01:24:30,516
I'm scared.

908
01:25:43,792 --> 01:25:45,657
Glad to see you're stirring around.

909
01:25:47,696 --> 01:25:50,529
Figured it was time.
I've been driving Michelle crazy.

910
01:25:50,599 --> 01:25:52,760
- Hey, kid.
- Say hi to your Uncle.

911
01:25:52,834 --> 01:25:54,426
Hi, Uncle Jesse.

912
01:25:55,937 --> 01:25:57,598
This is how you spent the money?

913
01:25:58,173 --> 01:26:01,370
This and the funeral.
There wasn't that much left.

914
01:26:02,344 --> 01:26:05,711
Me and Granddad figured
we'd get the bait shop up and going again.

915
01:26:05,814 --> 01:26:06,940
No kidding?

916
01:26:07,582 --> 01:26:09,106
Good for y'all.

917
01:26:16,825 --> 01:26:18,486
Steve, you know...

918
01:26:19,261 --> 01:26:22,355
...if I could trade places with Morgan, I would.

919
01:26:32,240 --> 01:26:33,969
Still feel like going out there?

920
01:26:36,244 --> 01:26:37,836
It's a good day for it.

921
01:27:25,026 --> 01:27:27,586
